{
  "texts": [
    "Cells in each sample were then finely clustered (Louvain algorithm, resolution = 10) and the average doublet score was calculated to identify small groups of similar doublets.",
    "Quality control filtering was done by applying the thresholds outlined in Supplementary Data 11.",
    "Integration of single-cell data.",
    "Samples were analyzed in two groups: healthy only and all conditions (healthy, regenerating, and embolized).",
    "Both groups were integrated using CSS 24."
  ]
}